    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワのステージ、凄く盛り上がってますね\n私の出番ももうすぐ……",
      "startTime": 10.9914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.1580724081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "緊張はしてるみたいだけど、いい顔をしてるな\nその様子なら大丈夫そうだ",
      "startTime": 17.5247390748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。莉央さんと歌うのは緊張しますけど……\nそれ以上に凄く頼もしくて、楽しみなんです",
      "startTime": 23.7580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5914057415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……お姉ちゃん、見てくれてるかな",
      "startTime": 28.5914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――これよりしばらく前",
      "startTime": 32.8580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.7914057415
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.7914057415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の合間にまで打ち合わせさせて悪いな、琴乃",
      "startTime": 35.8580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、月ストのアルバムを作らせてもらえるんですから\nこれくらい平気です",
      "startTime": 43.9580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.9247390748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それで……なんですけど。アルバムでどんなことが\nしたいか、みんなから意見をもらってきました",
      "startTime": 49.8580724081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、すずの案で各曲の月スト五人バージョンと\nすずのソロバージョンを入れたい……だそうです",
      "startTime": 59.0914057415,
      "sfxList": []
    }
